title: Virgil: Donald Trump, Rosie the Riveter, and the Revival of American Economic Nationalism
text: Trump: YPSILANTI, MI- MARCH 15: U.S. President Donald Trump speaks to auto workers at the American Center for Mobility March 15, 2017 in Ypsilanti, Michigan. Trump discussed his priorities of improving conditions to bolster the manufacturing industry and reduce the outsourcing of American jobs.
